OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,FParamilitary involvement in racist
OL,8,Fviolence has served to "exacerbate"
OL,9,Fanti-immigration unrest in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, an independent commission has
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FThe Independent Reporting Commission
OL,14,F(IRC), which was set up to monitor
OL,15,Fprogress toward ending paramilitarism
OL,16,Falso expressed concern that members of
OL,17,Fthe illegal terror groups were
OL,18,Fencouraging young people to get
OL,19,Finvolved in the disorder.
