OL,7,FWhile welcoming that "positive
OL,8,Fdevelopment", the commissioners
OL,9,Fcautioned that paramilitarism remained
OL,10,F"resilient" within communities in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland and they called for
OL,12,F"urgent" action to tackle the "live
OL,13,Fand serious" issues posed by the
OL,14,Fgroups.
