OL,3,CParamilitary involvement
OL,4,C'exacerbating' anti-immigration unrest
OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,F"The intimidation, coercive control
OL,8,Fand threats linked to paramilitary
OL,9,Fgroups persist, and the structures of
OL,10,Fparamilitary groups that continue
OL,11,Fintact can be used to facilitate
OL,12,Forganised crime and other forms of
OL,13,Fviolence," said the commissioners.
OL,15,F"A particularly serious manifestation
OL,16,Fof that reality over the last two
OL,17,Fyears has been the link between
OL,18,Fparamilitarism and racist violence
OL,19,Fconnected to the issue of immigration."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]wD@AOU{D@gO]
