OL,3,CParamilitary involvement
OL,4,C'exacerbating' anti-immigration unrest
OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,FThe reporting period fell outside the
OL,8,Fracist unrest that erupted in parts of
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland in June, but it did
OL,10,Fcover the anti-immigration unrest that
OL,11,Fflared the previous summer following
OL,12,Fthe Southport stabbings.
OL,14,FThe commissioners noted that race hate
OL,15,Fviolence had risen notably in 2024/25
OL,16,Fas they highlighted Police Service of
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland (PSNI) figures
OL,18,Fshowing that the period had witnessed
OL,19,Fthe highest number of instances in the
OL,20,F20 years such figures have been
OL,21,Frecorded.
