OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,FWhile police have said individuals
OL,8,Flinked to paramilitary groups have
OL,9,Fbeen involved in recent racist
OL,10,Fdisorder, officers have said there is
OL,11,Fno indication that the violence has
OL,12,Fbeen organised or sanctioned at a
OL,13,Fleadership level.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
