OL,3,CParamilitary involvement
OL,4,C'exacerbating' anti-immigration unrest
OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,FThe IRC report said: "The point is not
OL,8,Fwhether the involvement was
OL,9,F'organised' or not. The reality is
OL,10,Fthat the participation of individuals
OL,11,Fand groupings of individuals with
OL,12,Fclear links to paramilitarism in
OL,13,Fracist violence has undoubtedly served
OL,14,Fto exacerbate the situation in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland in terms of anti-
OL,16,Fimmigration unrest.
OL,26,@oD@VOU
