OL,3,CParamilitary involvement
OL,4,C'exacerbating' anti-immigration unrest
OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,F"This deeply worrying development...
OL,8,Fis further evidence of the risks
OL,9,Fattached to the continuation of
OL,10,Fparamilitarism and its structures, and
OL,11,Ffurther underlines the urgency on
OL,12,Fbringing it to an end.
OL,14,F"Another concerning factor in the
OL,15,Fracist unrest in Northern Ireland is
OL,16,Fthe level of involvement by young
OL,17,Fpeople."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@HO]
