OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,FThe commissioners said there had been
OL,8,Fprevious claims that paramilitaries
OL,9,Fhad exploited children by encouraging
OL,10,Fthem to take part in riots in 2021.
OL,12,FThey added: "Similar indicators of
OL,13,Fchild criminal exploitation are
OL,14,Falleged to have also been present in
OL,15,Fthe unrest during 2024/25. It is
OL,16,Fconcerning that so many children have
OL,17,Fcome into contact with the criminal
OL,18,Fjustice system as a result of their
OL,19,Finvolvement, and many do not appear to
OL,20,Funderstand the potential life-long
OL,21,Fconsequences of their actions."
