OL,7,FThe four IRC members are former US
OL,8,Fspecial envoy to Northern Ireland
OL,9,FMitchell Reiss, former human rights
OL,10,Fcommissioner and political leader
OL,11,FMonica McWilliams, solicitor John
OL,12,FMcBurney and former Irish diplomat Tim
OL,13,FO'Connor.
OL,15,FThe commissioners noted that a
OL,16,FStormont Executive programme to tackle
OL,17,Fparamilitarism and organised crime is
OL,18,Fdue to end in 2027.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
