OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,FThey stressed the need to continue to
OL,8,Finvest in efforts to combat
OL,9,Fparamilitary activity beyond that date.
OL,11,F"We recognise that the current fiscal
OL,12,Fenvironment is challenging; however,
OL,13,Fstrategic investment now will help
OL,14,Favoid significantly greater costs for
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland in the future," they
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@`O]
