OL,5,Cin NI
OL,7,F"If paramilitarism is not brought to
OL,8,Fan end, it will continue to create
OL,9,Funmanageable strain on public finances
OL,10,Fthrough its direct and indirect harms.
OL,11,FIn our engagement with victims and
OL,12,Fsurvivors, the overwhelming message
OL,13,Fhas been the prevention of any future
OL,14,Fharm. It is a key reason why the work
OL,15,Fof ending paramilitarism, once and for
OL,16,Fall, remains an urgent one."
