OL,7,FThe UK and Irish governments recently
OL,8,Fappointed an "interlocutor" to examine
OL,9,Fwhether a formal process of engagement
OL,10,Fwith paramilitary groups in Northern
OL,11,FIreland is required to bring about
OL,12,Ftheir disbandment.
OL,14,FThe move to appoint Fleur Ravensbergen
OL,15,Fcame after the IRC recommended the
OL,16,Fapproach.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@[O]
